               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18400106-name-214" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18400106-name-214" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18400106-name-214" type="surname" value="SAMWAYS"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18400106-name-214" type="given" value="SOPHIA"></interp>SOPHIA SAMWAYS.</persName>
                  </hi>I am the wife of James Sam ways, a messenger in the Treasury, living in Belgrave-place. I was robbed on the 2nd of No<lb></lb>vember—I have a garden in front, and they got over the iron palisades at the bottom of the garden, between eleven and three o'clock in the night, got into the area, cut the safe, and slipped the lock—I lost three brushes, a knife, and a piece of sirloin of beef—to the best of my knowledge I have seen my knife since—it is a pruning-knife—I have had it many years—this is it—(<hi rend="italic">examining it</hi>)—I have used it—these brushes are mine.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
