                  </hi>(<hi rend="italic">police-constable B</hi>158.) I apprehended the prisoner on the 22nd of December, about two o'clock in the morning—I found the brushes and knife in his house in the morning—he was taken into custody and locked up in the watch-house.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence</hi>. These brushes I bought in Berwick-court, about twelve months ago, and I can find a person who used them.</p>
